name: Cluster Products Pvt. Ltd.
overview:
Established in the year 2012, we, ‘Cluster Products Pvt. Ltd.’ are one of the reputed and well-established manufacturers, wholesalers and exporters of medical surgical disposable products that includes Surgical Gloves, Disposable Gloves, Disposable Face Masks, Disposable Caps, Surgical Gowns, Surgical Kits, Cord Clamps.

Our Products: Additionally, we offer a wide array of Sterile Surgical Gloves, Amazing Disposable Gloves, Disposable Long Sleeves Gloves, Disposable Face Mask, Non-Woven Medical Gown, Operation Theatre Kit, Disposable Surgeon Kit among others.

Our Competitive Age: We have highly modern manufacturing setup to develop high quality, safe and approved disposal products. Our company has adopted systematic and hygienic packaging process to maintain the quality and compete with the global medical standards. Moreover, continual R&D is done in this field to add value to our existing disposable product range.

Success Story: Cluster Product Pvt. Ltd is India’s first surgical manufacturing company with 50 Products. Started on 21st June 2012 and within 21 day came up with all his 50 products in Indian market.

Our Team: One of the most important factor that has always helped in the growth of the organisation is the highly qualified group of team-mates. These professionals are well versed with the current trends and industry’s standards.

Our Quality: We always make sure to deliver qualitative products at our customers’ end. Hence, we are considered as one of the prominent manufacturers of safe and effective medicines. The product range offered by us, is manufactured by ensuring various quality parameters.
